                  </hi>. I pursued and took the prisoner—he threw the bowl and money away—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was going to my uncle's, and meant to get a pint of beer, and saw a boy come out of the shop at the time—a man came and took me.</p>
